Class Lab3

  • java.lang.Object
    • lab3pkg.Lab3

  • public class Lab3
extends java.lang.Object
    This is the main class for the project which will test the data from dates.txt. Using this main class, the Date class, and the DateRange class, this program will create Date objects based off the data in dates.txt. It will then check if the next date is later that the previous date, and if so, will create a DateRange object to print out the timeframe between the two dates.
    Author:
    Marcus Lorenzana
